NightBlade:

     "Nobody uses me,' She said, holstering her weapon. Then she 
turned to Neptune. "and if you try you will die by my hand over the 
course of three days. Got it?"
     She turned back to SnowStalker. "I am sorry, but something 
inside is telling me to fight. But I promise that we will not."
